messageBody:
I have once recorded the shaw test piece text (discussed either here or on
the Shavian group) in my posh English accent (even though I'm Dutch) and in
the Dutch accent.

Here is where you can get them:

http://teraiten.myweb.nl/posh.mp3
http://teraiten.myweb.nl/dutch.mp3

I may have mispronounced some words, but that's because I have read more
words than I have heard, and because of my Dutch background. On the other
hand, I can pronounce a lot of sounds differently, because they happen in
Dutch (y, Y and o)

Ewout

/EvQt
